BUK TIMETABLE MANAGEMENT SYSTEM, FACULTY OF COMPUTING, BAYERO UNIVERSITY KANO.

 

 

 

 

ABDULLATEEF MOHAMMED KABIR

CST/18/IFT/00212


This BUK Timetable Management System has two parts, the users interface part for any one to see the content of the website and the admin interface part for the school administrators to add, edit and modify any content.

The website has the ability to generate printable PDF for all content including printing the Timetable, the list of staffs, departments, courses and classroom, everything on this website is user friendly.
